- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper proposes an unsupervised algorithm based on sequence prediction models, which are commonly used in machine learning.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel approach to phoneme segmentation using recurrent neural networks, which are a popular AI technique.
- cs.SI (Signal Processing) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the analysis of speech signals and their features.
